mysql-workbench

A MySQL visual database modeling, administration and querying tool

MySQL Workbench is a modeling tool that allows you to design and generate MySQL databases graphically. It also has administration and query development modules where you can manage MySQL server instances and execute SQL queries. This is the community build.

There is no official package available for openSUSE Leap 15.6
